<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk.Web">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netcoreapp3.1</TargetFramework>
	<GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
    <AssemblyName>ASI.ICT.BPMWebConsole</AssemblyName>
    <Description>This is a Web Console for monitoring the working status of BPM Server and the MQ communication between the server and airlines. Operators could do a reaction based on the response from this console dashboard, get statiscal reports, and send emails to notify the relative departments according to the alerting levels.

The version definition follows the "Semantic Versioning 2.0.0". The format of versioning is shown below
 - For Assembly Version: MAJOR.MINOR
 - For Assembly File Version: MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH
And the meaning of each indicator: 
 - MAJOR version when you make incompatible API changes,
 - MINOR version when you add functionality in a backwards compatible manner, and
 - PATCH version when you make backwards compatible bug fixes.</Description>
    <Company>CTCI ASI</Company>
    <Authors>KaiJyun Huang</Authors>
